---

## ğŸ” Features Implemented  

- OTP-based authentication for Signup and Password Reset  
- Secure 6-digit OTP generation with expiry  
- Limited OTP attempts for enhanced security  
- Readability Analysis Dashboard  
- Flesch Reading Ease  
- Flesch-Kincaid Grade  
- SMOG Index  
- Gunning Fog Index  
- Coleman-Liau Index  
- Word, sentence, syllable, and character count  
- Interactive gauge visualizations using Plotly  
- Password strength validation  
- Login rate limiting  
- Modern dark-themed UI  
- Fully tested and validated features  

